Multithreaded Chat Room

Name: Kushagra Arora
Roll Number: 2015049

This program implements a chat room that can handle upto 50 clients. The server accepts clients and the connected clients can talk to each other.

Compile :
javac -Xlint:deprecation Server_2015049r1.java
javac -Xlint:deprecation Client_2015049r1.java

Execute :
java ChatServer <portNumber>
java ChatClient <hostaddress> <portNumber>

